    "title": "OptimAI Claw: Launching Your First Native AI Agent in Seconds",
    "preview_text": "OptimAI Claw introduces a new paradigm in personal AI: native agents that live directly inside your node environment.\nNo external setup. No fragmented tooling. Just a persistent agent that can",
    "cover_url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HFED7U6bgAAiYHG.jpg",
    "content_state": {
      "blocks": [
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 61,
