            },
            {
              "length": 43,
              "offset": 193,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "d8ise",
          "text": "OptimAI Claw introduces a new paradigm in personal AI: native agents that live directly inside your node environment.\nNo external setup. No fragmented tooling. Just a persistent agent that can research, execute, and learn on your behalf.",
          "type": "blockquote"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "fgald",
          "text": "This guide walks through how to get started with OptimAI Claw inside your Core Node and begin running real workflows in seconds.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 46,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "cu568",
          "text": "Step 0: Install or Update OptimAI Core Node v2",
          "type": "header-two"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 20,
              "offset": 58,
              "style": "Bold"
            },
            {
              "length": 17,
              "offset": 102,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "78rb1",
          "text": "Before getting started, ensure you are running the latest OptimAI Core Node v2, now available on both Windows and macOS:",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": {
            "urls": [
              {
                "fromIndex": 2,
                "text": "https://optimai.network/optimai-nodes#nodes",
                "toIndex": 45
              }
            ]
          },
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 0,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            },
            {
              "key": 1,
              "length": 43,
              "offset": 2
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "b3cn7",
          "text": "👉 https://optimai.network/optimai-nodes#nodes",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 20,
              "offset": 84,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "kcok",
          "text": "If you already have OptimAI Nodes installed, no action is required -\nyour node will automatically update to the latest version.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 12,
              "offset": 24,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "91qkd",
          "text": "This version introduces OptimAI Claw, enabling native personal agents directly inside your node environment.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 41,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Italic"
            }
          ],
          "key": "6m1j5",
          "text": "(then your existing steps continue as-is)",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 26,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "2f9qj",
          "text": "Step 1: Open OptimAI Nodes",
          "type": "header-two"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 2,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "du17j",
          "text": " ",
          "type": "atomic"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "cffap",
          "text": "Start by launching your OptimAI Core Node on your device (Windows or macOS).\nEnsure your node is running normally.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 12,
              "offset": 28,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "detni",
          "text": "From the left sidebar, open OptimAI Claw.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "5h659",
          "text": "On first launch, the system may take a few moments to initialize your workspace. This is expected — the agent runtime is being prepared locally on your device.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 35,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "f7tm4",
          "text": "Step 2: Set Up Your Browser Profile",
          "type": "header-two"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 3,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "3u0ob",
          "text": " ",
          "type": "atomic"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 36,
              "offset": 31,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "2oapv",
          "text": "OptimAI Claw operates within a browser-native execution environment, allowing it to interact with real websites and workflows.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "61jh2",
          "text": "You’ll be prompted to either:",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "eo584",
          "text": "Import an existing browser profile (recommended for continuity), or",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "6ji4t",
          "text": "Start with a fresh profile (clean, isolated environment)",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "54jqk",
          "text": "Importing a profile enables Claw to operate with your familiar setup, including sessions and preferences.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 32,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "7hfmf",
          "text": "Step 3: Understand the Interface",
          "type": "header-two"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 4,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "dvd98",
          "text": " ",
          "type": "atomic"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 17,
              "offset": 34,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "bgnlp",
          "text": "OptimAI Claw is designed around a dual-panel system:",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 18,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "4uqjk",
          "text": "Chat Panel (left):\nWhere you define tasks, give instructions, and guide the agent.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 22,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "33e0g",
          "text": "Browser Panel (right):\nA live execution environment where you can observe Claw browsing, clicking, extracting data, and completing tasks in real time.",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 29,
              "offset": 26,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "ajjeb",
          "text": "This architecture ensures full transparency and control over agent actions.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 33,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "7jhks",
          "text": "Step 4: Start With a Clear Prompt",
