          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "brkp0",
          "text": "Self-improving agents",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "er6er",
          "text": "Proactive task execution",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "eam3k",
          "text": "Domain-specific utilities",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 28,
              "offset": 48,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "2t38p",
          "text": "This transforms Claw from a single agent into a programmable execution layer.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 10,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "3b9oc",
          "text": " ",
          "type": "atomic"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 17,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "c9k0e",
          "text": "What This Enables",
          "type": "header-two"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "djcn",
          "text": "With OptimAI Claw, your node is no longer just infrastructure.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "f1qq2",
          "text": "It becomes:",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 33,
              "offset": 2,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "lgv9",
          "text": "A persistent personal agent runtime",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 25,
              "offset": 20,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "239f6",
          "text": "A system capable of real-world task execution",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 39,
              "offset": 19,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "efbqp",
          "text": "A participant in a network of continuously learning agents",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 22,
              "offset": 26,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "cuhf1",
          "text": "This is the foundation of agent-native computing, where intelligence doesn’t just respond -- it operates.\n",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 11,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "dnsf",
          "text": " ",
          "type": "atomic"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "k57k",
          "text": "OptimAI Claw represents a shift from:",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 20,
              "offset": 27,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "98dsi",
          "text": "Prompt-based interaction → autonomous execution",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 29,
              "offset": 17,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "bqpoe",
          "text": "Isolated tools → integrated agent environments",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 29,
              "offset": 12,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "aqdgk",
          "text": "Static AI → continuously learning systems",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "eumbq",
          "text": "And it all starts directly from your node.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        }
